# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## v0.4.0 - 2025-04-11
### Fixed
- Fixed a bug preventing horizontal scrolling on the stats & settings page on mobile.

### Changed
- Added the save and back buttons to the top of the settings page as well.

## v0.3.0 - 2025-04-10
### Added
- Added additional but commented out families to the families.toml file.
- Updated README with section to describe how to supply custom families.toml. 
- Added horizontal scrolling support on the Stats & Settings page targeting mobile use.
- Added exponential backoff to iNaturalist API calls to handle large numbers of starting families.

## v0.2.0 - 2025-04-09
### Added
- Error handling for iNaturalist API errors, and show a message to the user that iNat is unavailable.

### Changed
- Base docker image up to python 3.14 slim.
- Updated GitHub actions to more recent versions.

## v0.1.1 - 2025-04-08
### Changed
- Reordered the Families section in the README to be lower.

### Fixed
- Updated the gunicorn entry point to correctly target the app when running the app with docker.

## v0.1.0 - 2026-04-08

### Added
- Beta version of the app.
- MIT license.
- README.md with attribution to the original book.
- Test suite with high coverage.
